data.value: The 2017 Honda Accord continues to uphold its reputation for reliability, sophistication, and performance in the midsize sedan segment. Powered by a robust 2.4-liter 4-cylinder engine, delivering 185 horsepower, the Accord offers a responsive and efficient driving experience. Paired with a seamless continuously variable transmission (CVT), it achieves an impressive EPA-estimated fuel economy of 27 mpg in the city and 36 mpg on the highway, ensuring cost-effective and enjoyable driving for all occasions. Its exterior design features a sleek silhouette and available 17-inch alloy wheels, projecting a sense of modernity and elegance. Inside, the Accord boasts a spacious and comfortable cabin with premium materials and intuitive technology, including a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Safety is paramount with features like Honda Sensing suite, encompassing collision mitigation braking and lane-keeping assist, providing peace of mind for drivers and passengers. With a mileage of 28,000 miles and a price of $17,000, the 2017 Honda Accord offers an exceptional balance of performance, refinement, and value for discerning drivers seeking a dependable and stylish sedan.
